{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"GlobalEventHandler.onanimationend","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/animationend_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概述","title":"概述","isH3":false,"content":"<p>事件处理程序。 当 CSS 动画到达其活动期的结束时发送此事件</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>animEndHandler</em> = <em>target</em>.onanimationend;\n\n<em>target</em>.onanimationend = <em>事件处理函数</em>\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"值","title":"值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>当<em><code>target</code></em>(HTML 元素， document 或者 window) 的 CSS 动画已经开始，<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/animationend_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">animationend (en-US)</a></code>事件会触发同时<code>事件处理函数</code>会被调用。<code>事件处理函数</code>会接收到唯一的参数：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a> 描述发生的事件。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>{{Page(\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onanimationstart\", \"Example\")}}</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spectable standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-animations-1/#eventdef-animationevent-animationend\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Animations Level 1<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">onanimationend</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.GlobalEventHandlers.onanimationend","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/A